= Script "ruby-biff"

This script pop-ups new mail notifications using growlnotify command.


= Requirement

Growl as well as growlnotify command is installed.
You may have to set PATH to growlnotify.


= Dependency

Requires the following Ruby libraries:
    highline

You can install them using gem:
    $ sudo gem install highline


= How to use

Just execute the following command:

    $ ruby /path/to/ruby-biff

You have to enter some information for the first time.
These configuration is stored to $HOME/.biff/config.yml.
